{
  "stem": "1736.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And did he live right near you and your parents?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was in the house next door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- it was a different times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were not going from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People-- the Kids used to play in the streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, there were a few motor cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can show you in the photo, the street, what it looked like, if you want to see it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, you know, people used to play.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I believe it was the same thing here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're talking 50 years ago.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People-- Kids used to play out in the street, and that's where you met other kids.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you used to play soccer, and you'd play this and that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, we had other playgrounds that we used to go to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, actually, there was another instance but I don't think I'll go into this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a lake there that used to get frozen over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one of the kids would try to push me into one of those holes at one stage.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it just came back to me right now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a lake called [NON-ENGLISH], and it was a lake that used to freeze over in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to go skating on that lake.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what others used to do is they used to make holes in it to get fish out of there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought-- I'm not sure whether, you know, how intentional it was, but-- it was intentional.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, I mean, how [INAUDIBLE] or if it was just a prank or all that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But kids try to shoved me down one of those holes at one stage, but I got away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was about-- this was the beginning of '38, like, in that winter.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
